description: Discovery and promotion of new music
overview:
tweewoo is a free music social media website decided to connecting music lovers with artists of all different types and styles from around the world. Offering free online radio stations where users can listen to over 20 different genres of music, follow their favorite artists and download free mp3.

Artists and labels can create their artist profiles from one single account and manage their music and information, upload tracks and pictures with a fast upload tool, post concert dates and videos and keep in touch with their fans via short messages.

Listeners can also create profiles to share their music tastes, post comments, follow artists and interact with them plus build a personalized radio based on artists they are following.
